data.description: Easy One Level Lake Living On Beloved Clear Lake Just Outside Ely, Set On apx 2.75 Acres of Majestic Pines & 800 Ft Lakeshore w/Opposite Shoreline Pristine Undeveloped State Land, Secluded Location On Dead End Rd.  This is a 112 acre private lake w/a carry down public access for canoes & small boats—beautiful small lake offering multiple use recreation near the BWCA. 2661 SF 3BR/3BA cedar sided home w/attached 2 stall gar, contractor built 1972 & numerous top quality updates over the years. Log wd burning sauna. Vaulted great rm w/full stone wall firepl, Oak hardwd flr, wall of lakefront Pella windows. Kitch w/island open to great rm & lakeside dining. Huge main flr lakeside primary bedroom w/private spa bath plus 2 large main flr guest bedrms. Walkout basement w/rec rm, bathrm, laundry. Zoned heat. Air cond. Metal roof.  Drilled well. See list of extensive updates. Click link for 3D Tour!
